      "text": [
        "3710 - وَ قَالَ اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"إِذَا مَاتَ اَلْمَيِّتُ حَلَّ مَا لَهُ وَ مَا عَلَيْهِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3710 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"When a deceased person dies, what he owes and what is owed to him become due.\""
        ]
      }
    }
